videos.headline: Troy's Marcus Jones takes opening kickoff to the house
videos.description: Marcus Jones goes untouched and takes the opening kickoff 96 yards for an early Troy touchdown vs. Coastal Carolina.

videos.headline: Troy gets tricky with WR-to-RB TD
videos.description: Troy receiver Luke Whittemore takes a lateral pass and airs it out to running back Jabir Daughtry-Frye for an easy 35-yard touchdown vs. Coastal Carolina.

videos.headline: Troy's B.J. Smith gains 47 yards, plunges in for TD
videos.description: Troy running back B.J. Smith sprints 47 yards down to the goal line, then takes it in from a yard out for another first quarter touchdown.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Outlow scores 4th-down TD
videos.description: Coastal Carolina goes for it on fourth-and-goal and Marcus Outlow punches it in to cut into Troy's lead.

videos.headline: Troy safety picks off Coastal Carolina
videos.description: Bryce Carpenter tries to force a pass that is intercepted by Troy safety Tyler Murray, who returns it 46 yards.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina QB gets hit, fires 10-yard TD
videos.description: Bryce Carpenter takes a hit but connects with Shadell Bell from 10 yards out for a Coastal Carolina touchdown.

videos.headline: Troy's Smith extends lead with 17-yard TD run
videos.description: B.J. Smith uses a stiff arm and scores his second touchdown from 17 yards out to put Troy back up by three scores.
